  "title": "Planning Engineer (Construction)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Supports Project Management schedulers by coordinating and planning project activities to meet timelines, deliverables, and milestones.</li>\n  <li>Develop, manage, and monitor baseline and working programme schedules, providing progress updates and ensuring alignment with project objectives.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and submit monthly payment requests, incorporating progress status and physical work completion, in collaboration with the various construction teams.</li>\n  <li>Conduct technical reviews, assist with tender submissions and claims, and oversee on-site safety and environmental compliance in accordance with contractual and regulatory requirements.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree/Diploma in a relevant Engineering, or Construction discipline</li>\n  <li>Minimal 2 years of planning experience in construction sector with either MS Project or Primavera/P6 proficiency</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If this opportunity aligns with your skills and experience, please submit your resume to <strong>koh.dickson@bayesrecruitment.com</strong></p>\n<p>Dickson KOH, EA Registration R1103367</p>\n<p>bayesrecruitment.com</p>",
